><hr size=1> I hope this is the spot for this request.  I was wondering if we could have an area where we can post questions about EQ. An area where we can draw upon each others expertise.  Many of us have knowledge about skills or abilities that we have learned and that knowledge might helpful to others.  Let me give an example of my two questions that I think others might have the answers to.<br>
1. I have failed to realize that ALL of my weapon skills should have been advanced while I was leveling.  Thinking that as a ranger I should only use 1H slashing skills, I failed to use my 2H skills.  Now I realize that 2H is important, it is taking me along time to advance it.  My question is ...It seems that the only time my 2H advances is when I use it against dark blue or higher mobs.  And that has cost me dearly in my selection of which MOB's to attack.  Is that true?  Can you only advance weapon skills against your lvl MOB or higher?<br>
2. I would like to know everyone's feelings about the AA points.  Some folks have told me to wait until lvl 60 before selecting a % for AA points. Other have told me to select anywhere from 10% to 90% as soon as you reach lvl 51.  I am really lost as to what is the best action for AA points.  I would like to hear what the &quot;Arrows&quot; think.<br>
<br>
These are just two questions I have.  Maybe others might have some also.<br>
<br>
Thanks for taking the time to respond. And Tymoria if I placed this request in the wrong spot.  Sorry.<br>
<br>
